data.description: Welcome home to 191 Natale Park Dr in Thibodaux! This beautifully kept, fully furnished, open floor plan home has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and a great open floor plan! The interior features include upgraded stainless appliances-all to remain with the home. It has ceramic tile flooring in the living area and all wet areas, granite countertops, and birch cabinets to name just a few. The exterior of the home features a relaxing screened in porch area to enjoy the weather and also a whole home generator! Don't miss your chance at the lovely home! Schedule a showing with your favorite realtor today! All measurements and zoning to be verified by buyer.
